Usage: write_module_model_context [-help] -cell <name>
                                  [-master_clone_inst <name>] [-tag <name>]
                                  -type {extraction_context timing_context}
                                  [-type_specific_options <string>]

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
-cell <name>                        # specifies the cell name of an instance
                                    # (string, required)
-master_clone_inst <name>           # specifies the instance name of an
                                    # master/clone. Use this option if the
                                    # instance has clone(s) (string, optional)
-tag <name>                         # specifies an output tag name. Default:
                                    # latest (string, optional)
-type {extraction_context timing_context}
                                    # <module model written out> (enum, required)
-type_specific_options <string>     # <type specific options>
                                    # (string, optional)